blog.name: art-in-distress
blog.title: *Screams Into The Void*
blog.description: Just an art student who wants to get their work out there. I AM currently accepting commissions, just message me for details! I don’t have any set prices because every piece is different, so like I said, don’t be afraid to message me! <3. I like to do fan art and original content too. My PayPal is PayPal.Me/ediefeldmann You can either donate money if you wish, or you can pay me here :) my Etsy is https://www.etsy.com/shop/ArtInDistress if you're interested in buying my stuff without having to talk to me. (Not all of my art is on there so PM or send me an anon if there’s a piece you want to purchase) This is also a discourse free zone, or I'll try to keep it as discourse free as possible
